full_text: Screened by NARA, 8/1/2023 UNITED STATES DEPARTMENT OF JUSTICE IMMIGRATION AND NATURALIZATION SERVICE Processing Sheet Application or File No. Petition Form No. DATA COLLECTION FOR ALIEN DOCUMENTATION, IDENTIFICATION & TELECOMMUNICATION SYSTEM (ADIT) Please print or type information requested below: COMPLETE NAME LIU, Chen COMPLETE MAILING ADDRESS (Include Zip Code) 20720 Community St. Canoga Park, Ca. 91306 MOTHER'S FIRST NAME Hsiao-Feng FATHER'S FIRST NAME Hsing-Tang CITY/TOWN/VILLAGE OF BIRTH Shong-Chen- CITY OF RESIDENCE WHEN APPLYING Los Angeles FOR A VISA OR IMMIGRANT STATUS CITY OF DESTINATION AT Los Angeles TIME OF ORIGINAL ADMISSION LOCATION OF CONSULATE WHERE IMMIGRANT VISA Los Angeles OBTAINED (OR IMMIGRATION OFFICE WHERE ADJUSTED) 11-16-11 DATE OF BIRTH PORT OF ENTRY WHEN ADMITTED AS IMMIGRANT OR Los Angeles OFFICE WHERE ADJUSTED TO LAWFUL PERMANENT RESIDENT SYMBOL ADMITTED UNDER (CLASSIFICATION) DATE ADMITTED OR ADJUSTED TO LAWFUL PERMANENT RESIDENT COUNTRY OF BIRTH China CARD NUMBER TRANSACTION NUMBER This form may be overprinted or stamped to show Instructions, items requested, items received, or other pertinent data which may facilitate processing. Keep this sheet on top of all material in file until Initial decision is made. FPI-LOM Form 1-468 (ADIT) 2-83 500 Tabs 5475 (Rav. 11.1.7m
